WEBVTT

00:00:01.081 --> 00:00:03.087
According to the UN,

00:00:03.111 --> 00:00:06.357
billions of people still live
without an address.

00:00:07.154 --> 00:00:09.435
The economist Hernando de Soto said,

00:00:09.459 --> 00:00:10.817
"Without an address,

00:00:10.841 --> 00:00:12.743
you live outside the law.

00:00:12.767 --> 00:00:14.385
You might as well not exist."

00:00:15.679 --> 00:00:18.830
I'm here to tell you how my team and I
are trying to change that.

00:00:19.986 --> 00:00:23.202
If you go to an online map
and look at a favela in Brazil

00:00:23.226 --> 00:00:25.050
or a township in South Africa,

00:00:25.074 --> 00:00:28.053
you'll see a few streets
but a lot of empty space.

